'''Featurepics''' is a [[royalty-free]] [[microstock photography]] digital content agency that has been actively working in the [[stock photography]] market since 2007 based in [[Fremont, California]]. <ref name="Bright Hub 2010-08-25">[http://www.brighthub.com/multimedia/photography/reviews/84173.aspx " Small Microstock Agencies: Feature Pics, 123rf, Scandinavian Stock, and CanStockPhoto"], Bright Hub August 25, 2010</ref> <ref name="Microstock Diaries 2007-04-25">[http://www.microstockdiaries.com/featurepics.html "Featurepics review"], Microstock Diaries April 25, 2007</ref>
Featurepics has successfully developed solid and efficient content library of over 3 million [[royalty-free]] [[photographs]], [[vector images]], [[illustrations]] as well as an established network of partners across the media industry.<ref name="Microstockinsider 2008-04-18">[http://microstockinsider.com/site_reviews/featurepicscom "Featurepics.com Review"], Microstockinsider April 18, 2008</ref> Featurepics utilizes a unique business model is to provide users with an inventory of high-quality images licensed for specific uses ([[Royalty-free]], [[publications]], [[software]], etc.).<ref name="Stock Photo Talks 2008-11-07">[http://www.stockphototalk.com/the_stock_photo_industry_/2008/12/featurepicscom-announces-new-alternative-to-stock-photo-subscription-model.html#more "FeaturePics.com Announces New Alternative to Stock Photo Subscription Model"], Stock Photo Talk December 07, 2008</ref> Featurepics provides content API portal to distribute a variety of [[stock photos]] with helpful HTML codes for linking across individual images and entire portfolios. With the help from its contributors the site categorizes graphics media to provide designers with variety of resources, from basic stock content to custom graphics concepts <ref name="Creative Publishing Network 2008-07-29">[http://creativepro.com/featurepicscom-announces-new-search-tools/ "FeaturePics.com Announces New Search Tools"], Creative Publishing July 29, 2008</ref> in direct competition with [[Shutterstock]] and [[Alamy]] agencies.<ref name="Shout About Art 2008-07-16">[https://theartisansshout.wordpress.com/about/feature-pics-for-photographers-for-artists-for-buyers/ "Feature Pics: For Photographers, For Artists, For Buyers"], Shout About Art July 16, 2008</ref>
